"42:19:4" : {s: 42, a: 19, w: 4, r: "رزق", t: "يَرْزُقُ", l: "رَزَقَ", lc: 61, tl: "yarzuqu", lb: "যোগানো, সংস্থান দেওয়া, সরবরাহ করা",e: "He gives provision", b: "তিনি সংস্থান/রিজিক দেন", i: "Dia memberi rezeki", f: 4, rm: "to provide, supply, bestow, grant, means of subsistance. turzaqan - you both shall be supplied. rizq - bounty, gift, portion/share. raziq - one who provides or supplies. razzaq  -great provider/supplier.", ag: "فعل مضارع ", eg: "Verb Imperfect ", tag: "V", pos: "V", att: "IMPF", qual: "", deg: "3", gen: "M", num: "S", mood: "", lu: "رِزْقٌۭ"},
